    <h2 class="section-title">What we do, and what we send to other trades.</h2>

    <p><strong>We service:</strong> all gas fireplace makes and models, direct-vent inserts, vent-free units, B-vent, see-through, linear/contemporary, outdoor-rated. Indoor and outdoor. Residential and commercial (restaurant ambiance fireplaces).</p>

    <p><strong>We don't service:</strong> wood-burning fireplaces or wood-fired pizza ovens. SCAQMD Rule 445 makes new wood-burning installations restricted across most of SoCal, and existing wood-burning fireplace repair is largely chimney sweep + masonry trade, not appliance repair. Most retrofits we see are gas conversions, converting an existing wood-burning fireplace to a gas insert. We do those.</p>

    <p><strong>We don't do:</strong> chimney sweeping/masonry, electric fireplace repair (different trade, mostly throwaway/replace economics), brand-new gas line installation from the meter (plumber trade).</p>
